# macOS
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Secrets — never commit
.env
**/.env
.handoff-secrets.yaml
**/.handoff-secrets.yaml

# Runtime state / bind-mount data (back up separately, don't version)
**/data/
**/db/
**/redis/
**/cache/

__pycache__/

# iCloud Drive "Desktop & Documents" conflict copies: this repo lives under
# ~/Documents which is iCloud-synced, and rapid page regeneration spawns
# "name 2.md" / "name 3.md" duplicates. Never track them.
* [0-9].*
* [0-9][0-9].*
